OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,FMetro Mayor Steve Rotheram has
OL,8,Fannounced #2 billion of investment for
OL,9,Fthe Liverpool City Region.
OL,11,FInitial investments will focus on
OL,12,Fdelivering office space in the city
OL,13,Fcentre as well as lab space across the
OL,14,Fwider city region.
OL,16,FThe funding is expected to create jobs
OL,17,Fand "accelerate economic growth across
OL,18,Fthe region".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
