PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,FMayor Steve Rotheram unveiled the
OL,8,Finvestment at MIPIM, the world's
OL,9,Fleading real estate event, where the
OL,10,FLiverpool City Region is showcasing
OL,11,Fmore than #11bn of investment
OL,12,Fopportunities to international
OL,13,Finvestors.
OL,15,FHe said: "Anyone who knows this region
OL,16,Fknows we've never been short of
OL,17,Fambition - what we've sometimes lacked
OL,18,Fare the tools and funding to turn that
OL,19,Fambition into reality. Over the last
OL,20,Ffew years, however, devolution has
OL,21,Fstarted to change that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,F"We've been able to put our money
OL,8,Fwhere our mouth is and invest in
OL,9,Fthings that really matter to people
OL,10,Fhere - new train stations, a publicly
OL,11,Fowned fleet of trains, multi-modal
OL,12,Finterchanges, a fast-growing digital
OL,13,Fnetwork and tens of thousands of new
OL,14,Fjobs and apprenticeships.
OL,16,F"In short, all of the ingredients to
OL,17,Fmake the Liverpool City Region the
OL,18,Fbest place to grow up, grow a business
OL,19,Fand grow a family."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,FThe fund forms a part of the region's
OL,8,Flong-term plan to grow the economy by
OL,9,F#10bn over the next decade,
OL,10,F"strengthening its position as one of
OL,11,Fthe UK's leading centres for
OL,12,Finnovation and advanced manufacturing."
OL,14,FThe planned investment is expected to
OL,15,Fhelp sectors including advanced
OL,16,Fmanufacturing, life sciences and
OL,17,Fdigital technology.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,FIt is also expected to deliver up to
OL,8,F64,000 new homes and the
OL,9,Finfrastructure needed to support
OL,10,Fgrowing communities.
OL,12,FRotheram said: "We all know there's
OL,13,Fstill so much more potential waiting
OL,14,Fto be unlocked. Too many sites have
OL,15,Fstood still for years, too many
OL,16,Fopportunities have passed us by, and
OL,17,Ftoo many talented young people have
OL,18,Ffelt they've had to leave the region
OL,19,Fto get on in life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,F"Well no longer. With this #2bn
OL,8,FInvestment Fund we're setting out to
OL,9,Fchange that - giving us the firepower
OL,10,Fto unlock development, build the homes
OL,11,Fpeople need and back the industries
OL,12,Fthat will create the next generation
OL,13,Fof good, well-paid jobs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773191770
OL,3,CLiverpool City Region announces
OL,4,Clargest ever investment which could
OL,5,Cboost jobs
OL,7,F"The Liverpool City Region has always
OL,8,Fbeen a place that looks outward -
OL,9,Ftrading, creating and innovating with
OL,10,Fthe rest of the world. What we're
OL,11,Fsaying at MIPIM this week is simple:
OL,12,Fif you want to be part of what comes
OL,13,Fnext for this region, now's the time
OL,14,Fto get involved."
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
